### ==========================================
### 项目模块 API 测试
### ==========================================

### 0. 获取 Token
# @name login
POST http://localhost:18081/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "XiyuAdmin2026!"
}

@token = {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### 1. 正常流程：项目列表
GET http://localhost:18081/api/projects?page=0&size=10&sort=createdAt,desc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. 正常流程：创建项目
POST http://localhost:18081/api/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "API测试项目-{{$randomInt 1 9999}}",
  "description": "通过 API 测试创建的项目",
  "status": "BIDDING"
}

@projectId = 1

### 3. 正常流程：项目详情
GET http://localhost:18081/api/projects/{{projectId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. 边界：不存在项目
GET http://localhost:18081/api/projects/999999
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. 边界：创建项目缺少名称
POST http://localhost:18081/api/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "缺少项目名称"
}

### 6. 正常流程：评分预览
POST http://localhost:18081/api/projects/score-preview
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "estimatedBudget": 5000000,
  "industryCategory": "IT",
  "projectComplexity": "HIGH",
  "tags": ["技术方案", "集成服务"],
  "evaluationRules": {
    "minTechScore": 70,
    "minFinanceScore": 60,
    "requiredExperience": "3年以上同类项目经验"
  }
}

### 7. 正常流程：招标文件分解就绪检查
GET http://localhost:18081/api/projects/{{projectId}}/tender-breakdown/readiness
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. 正常流程：AI 卡片
GET http://localhost:18081/api/projects/{{projectId}}/ai-cards
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. 正常流程：任务分解
GET http://localhost:18081/api/projects/{{projectId}}/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10. 边界：空项目列表
GET http://localhost:18081/api/projects?page=0&size=10&name=__nonexistent_project_name__
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
